<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id80ea69da-3a70-11f1-b817-c08bf6d1fe2c" identifier="/us/usc/t40/s17705"><num value="17705">§ 17705.</num><heading> Approval of Federal Communications Commission</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">A transfer under this chapter does not require the approval of the Federal Communications Commission except to the extent that the approval of the Commission is necessary under <ref href="/us/usc/t40/s17704/3">section 17704(3) of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id80ecd9db-3a70-11f1-b817-c08bf6d1fe2c">(<ref href="/us/pl/107/217">Pub. L. 107–217</ref>, <date date="2002-08-21">Aug. 21, 2002</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/116/1288">116 Stat. 1288</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
